title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 7 categories of Frequency on the x axis representing 4 groups: White, Hispanic, Black, and Other.
Averaging these 4 groups, the highest category is found for Frequency At least once a day with a mean value of 55.5.
The lowest category is observed at Don't know/No opinion that has a mean value of 2.5
showing a difference of 182.8% with the maximum value.

In case of At least once a day, White shows more dominance than any other Frequency with a value 64.0 and it has the lowest value 2.0 in Don't know/No opinion.  However, Other being the 2nd most important group, has the highest value 49.0 for Frequency At least once a day and the lowest 2.0 in case of Don't know/No opinion.
